      "acceptanceCriteria": "Input parameters must be documented; sensitivity analysis not required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "All model input parameters including fluid viscosity, density, hemolysis model coefficients, and boundary conditions were documented in the simulation report. Formal sensitivity analysis is not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
