      "acceptanceCriteria": "Correspondence between simulation input parameters and experimental conditions must be documented; formal equivalency analysis not required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Simulation boundary conditions were mapped to experimental conditions by direct correspondence of flow rate, rotational speed, and fluid properties. Formal equivalency uncertainty analysis is not required at MRL 2."
